# VEHICLE::GET_HELI_TAIL_ROTOR_HEALTH

## Summary
Returns the health of the heli tail rotor

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle

## Returns
* **FLOAT**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Max 1000.
At 0 the tail rotor will stall.
